               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910413-40-cd224" type="crimeDate">21st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-40-off223 t17910413-40-cd224"></join>, four hundred pounds weight of lead, value 40 s. from the parish church of Stepney
